nodes.text: Bilbringi Depot was the primary settlement of Bilbringi VII, the largest asteroid of the Bilbringi system, during the Clone Wars. It was owned by Drixo the Hutt, who around 21 BBY lost custody of the depot to the bounty hunter Cad Bane, who secured it for Darth Sidious and the Techno Union. It was later liberated by the Galactic Republic's Breakout Squad, who captured Overseer Umbrag.
